job.title: Punjab State Cooperative Bank Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 856 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:856

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Senior manager
  • Manager
  • Information Technology Officer
  • Clerk cum DEO
  • Steno Typist

Description

New Indian Government Jobs have been published by Punjab State Cooperative Bank for various vacancies in Punjab. If you are finding a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in India, from now on, and till the 20-05-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for SC/ST candidates is only Rs. 700/-.
  • The application fee for the rest of the candidates is only Rs. 1400/-.

Important dates

  •  The last date to apply in these vacancies is 04-06-2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 37  years old. 

Detailed vacancies:

Punjab State Cooperative Bank Pay Scale

According to the information given by the Indian Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is given below.

  • Senior Manager - Rs. 35400
  • Manager - Rs. 29200
  • Information and Technology Officer - Rs. 25500
  • Steno-Typist. - Rs. 21700
  • Clerk-cum-Data Entry Operator - Rs. 19900

How to apply for Punjab State Cooperative Bank Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in India. Fill in your details and submit it

Or follow all the steps given below,

  •  First, go to the official website of Punjab State Cooperative Bank and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Punjab State Cooperative Bank.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
